Financial Stock Exchange app implemented with Play Framework.

It uses Mysql as persistency layer so database,user creation needed. Then configure application with conf/application.conf

Application support one transaction at a time so be carefull with conqurrent requests. Database locking can be usefull to solve it.

Application assumes transactions are ordered in time.  

Transactions backed by events. Each transactions can be generated by event replaying. See the transaction_events table.

To run 

```
activator run
```
